description: A cropdusting plane with a fear of heights lives his dream of competing in a famous around-the-world aerial race.

title: Bambi
description: The story of a young deer growing up in the forest.

title: Minions & More 1
description: This collection of Minions shorts from the "Despicable Me" franchise includes mini-movies like "Training Wheels," "Puppy" and "Yellow Is the New Black."

title: Porco Rosso
description: In 1930s Italy, a veteran World War I pilot is cursed to look like an anthropomorphic pig.

title: Igor
description: Told from Igor's perspective, we see the troubled young assistant's dark origins, his redemptive friendship with the young medical student Viktor Von Frankenstein, and become eyewitnesses to the emergence of how Frankenstein became the man - and the legend - we know today.

title: The Great Mouse Detective
description: Basil, the rodent Sherlock Holmes, investigates the kidnapping of a toy maker and uncovers its link to his archenemy, Professor Ratigan.

title: Batman: The Long Halloween, Part Two
description: The killer known as Holiday continues to stalk the Falcone crime family while a new class of costumed criminal rises in Gotham City. Batman suspects that a former ally might be the serial killer.

title: Persepolis
description: A precocious and outspoken Iranian girl grows up during the Islamic Revolution.

title: Mia and Me: The Hero of Centopia
description: Mia discovers her magic stone is part of an ancient prophecy and embarks on a thrilling journey to the farthest islands of Centopia to face a great evil, and shape her own destiny.

title: The Angry Birds Movie 2
description: The flightless birds and scheming green pigs take their feud to the next level.

title: The Garden of Words
description: A 15-year-old boy and 27-year-old woman find an unlikely friendship one rainy day in the Shinjuku Gyoen National Garden.

title: The Lego Ninjago Movie
description: Shunned by everyone for being the son of an evil warlord, a teenager seeks to defeat him with the help of his fellow ninjas.

title: My Little Pony: A New Generation
description: After the time of the Mane 6, Sunny--a young Earth Pony--and her new Unicorn friend Izzy explore their world and strive to restore Harmony to Equestria.

title: Red Shoes and the Seven Dwarfs
description: Princes who have been turned into Dwarfs seek the red shoes of a lady in order to break the spell, although it will not be easy. A parody with a twist.

title: The Wolf House
description: Tells the story of Maria, a young woman who takes refuge in a house in southern Chile after escaping from a German colony.

title: Anomalisa
description: A man crippled by the mundanity of his life experiences something out of the ordinary.

title: G-Force
description: A specially trained squad of guinea pigs is dispatched to stop a diabolical billionaire from taking over the world.

title: Smurfs: The Lost Village
description: In this fully animated, all-new take on the Smurfs, a mysterious map sets Smurfette and her friends Brainy, Clumsy, and Hefty on an exciting race through the Forbidden Forest, leading to the discovery of the biggest secret in Smurf history.

title: Pokémon: The First Movie - Mewtwo Strikes Back
description: Scientists genetically create a new Pokémon, Mewtwo, but the results are horrific and disastrous.

title: When Marnie Was There
description: Due to 12 y.o. Anna's asthma, she's sent to stay with relatives of her guardian in the Japanese countryside. She likes to be alone, sketching. She befriends Marnie. Who is the mysterious, blonde Marnie.

title: Diary of a Wimpy Kid: Rodrick Rules
description: Back in middle school after summer vacation, Greg Heffley and his older brother Rodrick must deal with their parents' misguided attempts to have them bond.

title: Catwoman: Hunted
description: Follows Catwoman in an attempt to steal a priceless jewel. This puts her squarely in the crosshairs of both a powerful consortium of villains, Interpol and Batwoman.

title: Curious George
description: The Man in the Yellow Hat is an oddball museum employee who looks after his pet monkey, an inquisitive and wonderful creature whose enthusiasm often gets the best of him.

title: From Up on Poppy Hill
description: A group of Yokohama teens look to save their school's clubhouse from the wrecking ball in preparations for the 1964 Tokyo Olympics.

title: The Swan Princess
description: A power-hungry sorcerer curses a princess to live as a swan by day in this tale of everlasting love.

title: The Many Adventures of Winnie the Pooh
description: In this collection of animated shorts based on the stories and characters by A.A. Milne, Winnie the Pooh, a honey-loving teddy bear, embarks on some eccentric adventures.

title: Animal Farm
description: A successful farmyard revolution by the resident animals vs. the farmer goes horribly wrong as the victors create a new tyranny among themselves.

title: Vampire Hunter D: Bloodlust
description: When a girl is abducted by a vampire, a legendary bounty hunter is hired to bring her back.

title: Tom and Jerry: The Movie
description: Cat and mouse duo Tom and Jerry reluctantly work together to save a young girl from her evil aunt.

title: The Last: Naruto the Movie
description: Hinata Hyuga's younger sister has been kidnapped, so Naruto must do what he can to save her.
